    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "Every morning now brought its regular duties-shops were to be visited; some new part of the town to be looked at; and the pump room to be attended, where they paraded up and down for an hour, looking at everybody and speaking to no one.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "The wish of a numerous acquaintance in Bath was still uppermost with mrs Allen, and she repeated it after every fresh proof, which every morning brought, of her knowing nobody at all.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "They made their appearance in the Lower Rooms; and here fortune was more favourable to our heroine.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000002_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000002_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "His address was good, and Catherine felt herself in high luck.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000002_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000002_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "There was little leisure for speaking while they danced; but when they were seated at tea, she found him as agreeable as she had already given him credit for being.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000002_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000002_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "He talked with fluency and spirit-and there was an archness and pleasantry in his manner which interested, though it was hardly understood by her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000002_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000002_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "I have been very negligent-but are you now at leisure to satisfy me in these particulars?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000002_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000002_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "If you are I will begin directly.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"You need not give yourself that trouble, sir.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"About a week, sir,\" replied Catherine, trying not to laugh.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"Really!\" with affected astonishment.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"Why should you be surprised, sir?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"Why, indeed!\" said he, in his natural tone.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"But some emotion must appear to be raised by your reply, and surprise is more easily assumed, and not less reasonable than any other.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "Now let us go on.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"Indeed!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"Yes, sir, I was there last Monday.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"Have you been to the theatre?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"Yes, sir, I was at the play on Tuesday.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"To the concert?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"Yes, sir, on Wednesday.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"And are you altogether pleased with Bath?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"Yes-I like it very well.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"Now I must give one smirk, and then we may be rational again.\" Catherine turned away her head, not knowing whether she might venture to laugh.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"I see what you think of me,\" said he gravely-\"I shall make but a poor figure in your journal tomorrow.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"Indeed I shall say no such thing.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"Shall I tell you what you ought to say?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"If you please.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "That, madam, is what I wish you to say.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"But, perhaps, I keep no journal.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"Perhaps you are not sitting in this room, and I am not sitting by you.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "Not keep a journal!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000026_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000026_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "How are the civilities and compliments of every day to be related as they ought to be, unless noted down every evening in a journal?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000026_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000026_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "How are your various dresses to be remembered, and the particular state of your complexion, and curl of your hair to be described in all their diversities, without having constant recourse to a journal?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000026_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000026_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "My dear madam, I am not so ignorant of young ladies' ways as you wish to believe me; it is this delightful habit of journaling which largely contributes to form the easy style of writing for which ladies are so generally celebrated.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000026_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000026_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "Everybody allows that the talent of writing agreeable letters is peculiarly female.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000026_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000026_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "Nature may have done something, but I am sure it must be essentially assisted by the practice of keeping a journal.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"I have sometimes thought,\" said Catherine, doubtingly, \"whether ladies do write so much better letters than gentlemen!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "That is-I should not think the superiority was always on our side.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000029_000000",
