        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "You do not think too highly of us in that way.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"I should no more lay it down as a general rule that women write better letters than men, than that they sing better duets, or draw better landscapes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "In every power, of which taste is the foundation, excellence is pretty fairly divided between the sexes.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
