        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"I hope I am, madam.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"And pray, sir, what do you think of Miss Morland's gown?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"It is very pretty, madam,\" said he, gravely examining it; \"but I do not think it will wash well; I am afraid it will fray.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"How can you,\" said Catherine, laughing, \"be so-\" She had almost said \"strange.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"I am quite of your opinion, sir,\" replied mrs Allen; \"and so I told Miss Morland when she bought it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "\"But then you know, madam, muslin always turns to some account or other; Miss Morland will get enough out of it for a handkerchief, or a cap, or a cloak.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000043_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000043_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "Muslin can never be said to be wasted.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-173_200_000043_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/173/200/173_200_000043_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-173",
        "content": "I have heard my sister say so forty times, when she has been extravagant in buying more than she wanted, or careless in cutting it to pieces.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
